span>お電話でのお問い合わせ</span></p>\n\t\t\t<a href=\"tel:076-403-9010\">\n\t\t\t\t<p class=\"d-none\">076-403-9010</p>\n\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"phone-time\">受付時間　平日 9:00-17:00</p>\n\t\t</li>\n\t</ul>\n\n\t<p class=\"others-btn\"><a href=\"/inquiry/\"><span>採用・その他のお問い合わせ</span></a></p>\n</div><!-- class=\"menu-tel\" -->\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"h-entry-btn-area\">\n\t<p class=\"btn-entry\"><a href=\"/job-info/\" class=\"b-bl\"><span>募集要項</span></a></p>\n\t<p class=\"btn-entry\"><a href=\"/inquiry/\" class=\"b-pk\"><span>ENTRY</span></a></p>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--class=\"sub\"-->\n\n</div><!-- id=\"header-main\" -->\n\n\n</header>\n\n\n\n\n<div id=\"content\">\n\n<main role=\"main\" id=\"alpha\">\n\n\n<div class=\"bg-bokashi\"><!-- class=\"bg-bokashi\" 背景のぼかし -->\n\n\n<article id=\"home-mv\" class=\"home-mv-area\">\n\n<section class=\"main-mv-area\">\n\t<div class=\"main-mv-box\">\n\t\t<p class=\"main-mv\">\n\t\t\t<video autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"/common/movie/poster.webp\">\n\t\t\t<source src=\"/common/movie/recruit-top_ver2.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n\t\t\t<!-- ↓ 動画が再生できなかったときの代替表示 -->\n\t\t\t<img src=\"/common/movie/samune.webp\" alt=\"フォールバック画像\">\n\t\t\tお使いのブラウザは video タグに対応していません。\n\t\t\t</video>\n\t\t</p>\n\t</div>\n\t<div class=\"lottie-mv-txt\"></div>\n</section>\n\n<div class=\"container\">\n\t<p class=\"more-movie-button\">\n\t\t<a class=\"youtube-icon glightbox\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LYp61WBJxy4\" data-gallery=\"custom-movie\" data-type=\"video\" data-source=\"youtube\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"text\">MORE MOVIE</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"circle\">\n\t\t\t\t<span class=\"arrow\"></span>\n\t\t\t\t<span class=\"spinner\"></span>\n\t\t\t</span>\n\t\t</a>\n\t</p>\n</div>\n\n</article><!-- id=\"home-mv\" -->\n\n\n\n<article id=\"jops-message\">\n\n<div class=\"container\">\n<section class=\"jops-msg-area\">\n\n<div class=\"fukidashi-box\">\n\t<p class=\"msg-txt\">\n\t\t<span class=\"marker\">仕事を楽しみ、お客様の喜びに換え、<br class=\"d-sm-none\">やがて社会が笑顔になる。</span>\n\t</p>\n\n\t<div class=\"j-msg-logo-area\">\n\t\t<p class=\"j-msg-logo\"><img src=\"../common/images/parts/menu-logo-c-01.svg\" alt=\"JOPSロゴ\"></p>\n\t</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"j-meaning-area\">\n\t<p>JOPSは “３つの楽しい”  を<br class=\"d-sm-none\">大切にしている会社です。<br class=\"d-none d-sm-inline\">\n\t私たちが目指すのは、<br class=\"d-sm-none\">関わるすべての人が笑顔になれる未来。<br>\n\tあなたも、私たちと一緒に<br class=\"d-sm-none\">「楽しい」をつなぐ仲間になりませんか？</p>\n</div>\n\n</section><!-- class=\"jops-msg-area\" -->\n</div><!-- class=\"container\" -->\n\n\n<section class=\"top-loop-slider\">\n\t<ul>\n\t\t<li class=\"skshi\"><img src=\"../common/images/top/00-00-01-01.webp\" alt=\"スライド1\"></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"skshi\"><img src=\"../common/images/top/00-00-01-02.webp\" alt=\"スライド2\"></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"skshi\"><img src=\"../common/images/top/00-00-01-03.webp\" alt=\"スライド3\"></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"skshi\"><img src=\"../common/images/top/00-00-01-04.webp\" alt=\"スライド4\"></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"skshi\"><img src=\"../common/images/top/00-00-01-05.webp\" alt=\"スライド5\"></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"skshi\"><img src=\"../common/images/top/00-00-01-06.webp\" alt=\"スライド6\"></li>\n\t</ul>\n\t<ul>\n\t\t<li class=\"skshi\"><img src=\"../common/images/top/00-00-01-01.webp\" alt=\"スライド1\"></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"skshi\"><img src=\"../common/images/top/00-00-01-02.webp\" alt=\"スライド2\"></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"skshi\"><img src=\"../common/images/top/00-00-01-03.webp\" alt=\"スライド3\"></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"skshi\"><img src=\"../common/images/top/00-00-01-04.webp\" alt=\"スライド4\"></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"skshi\"><img src=\"../common/images/top/00-00-01-05.webp\" alt=\"スライド5\"></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"skshi\"><img src=\"../common/images/top/00-00-01-06.webp\" alt=\"スライド6\"></li>\n\t</ul>\n</section><!-- class=\"top-loop-slider\" -->\n\n</article><!-- id=\"jops-message\" -->\n\n\n\n<article id=\"jops-about\" class=\"mb-area\">\n\n<section class=\"j-about-area\">\n\n<div class=\"j-about-box_overflow\">\n\n\t<div class=\"j-about-box\">\n\t<p class=\"deco-en\">Japan  <br class=\"d-md-none\">Open  <br class=\"d-md-none\">Systems</p>\n\n\t\t<p class=\"giza-marker\"></p>\n\t\t<p class=\"j-abox-ilist\"><img src=\"../common/images/top/ilist-00-01.png\" alt=\"JOPSを知るイラスト\"></p>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"j-about-txt-area\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"title-a\">JOPSを知る</h2>\n\t\t\t<ul class=\"j-tag-list\">\n\t\t\t\t<li><p><a href=\"/about/#solution\"><span>＃仕事内容</span></a></p></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li><p><a href=\"/about/#pl-mission\"><span>＃MISSION</span></a></p></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li><p><a href=\"/about/#pl-message\"><span>＃代表メッセージ</span></a></p></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li><p><a href=\"/about/#strengths\"><span>＃JOPSの強み</span></a></p></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li><p><a href=\"/about/#scale\"><span>＃JOPSのスケール</span></a></p></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li><p><a href=\"/about/#young-voice\"><span>＃社内アンケート</span></a></p></li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"j-txt\">JOPSは独立系IT企業として、DXやクラウド、IoTなど多彩な分野で社会に貢献。社員の技術力を強みに、働きがいと成長が両立する環境を築いています。</p>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"btn-continue d-none d-xl-block\"><a href=\"/about/\" class=\"cntn-bl\"><span>詳しく知る</span></a></p>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"circle-btn-area\">\n\t<div class=\"circle-btn\">\n\t\t<p><img src=\"../common/images/parts/jpos-circle-bk.svg\" alt=\"JOPSを知る\" class=\"loop-btn-en\"></p>\n\t\t<a href=\"/about/\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"circle-txt\"><span>JOPSを知る</span></p>\n\t\t</a>\n\t</div>\n</div>\n\n</section><!-- class=\"j-about-area\" -->\n\n</article><!-- id=\"jops-about\" -->\n\n</div><!-- class=\"bg-bokashi\" 背景のぼかし -->\n\n\n\n<div class=\"bg-bokashi\"><!-- class=\"bg-bokashi\" 背景のぼかし -->\n\n<article id=\"top-works\">\n\n<section class=\"top-works-area\">\n\t<p class=\"top-works-photo js-trigger\"><img src=\"../common/images/top/00-00-03-01.webp\" alt=\"はたらく環境\"></p>\n\n\t<div class=\"top-wks-box-area\">\n\n\t\t<div class=\"top-wks-box-wh\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"giza-marker\"></p>\n\n\t\t\t<div class=\"top-works-txt-area\">\n\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"title-a\">はたらく環境</h2>\n\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"j-tag-list\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<li><p><a href=\"/work-style/#works-vr\"><span>＃VR新社屋体験</span></a></p></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li><p><a href=\"/work-style/#office\"><span>＃全国の事業所</span></a></p></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li><p><a href=\"/work-style/#ease-of-working\"><span>＃働きやすさについて</span></a></p></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li><p><a href=\"/work-style/#step-up\"><span>＃キャリアステップ</span></a></p></li>\n\t\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t\t<p class=\"j-txt\">テレワークやフレックス制度などの多様な働き方や、女性活躍や子育て支援などの働きやすさと人を大切にする職場づくりを実践しています。</p>\n\t\t\t\t<p class=\"btn-continue\"><a href=\"/work-style/\" class=\"cntn-bl\"><span>詳しく知る</span></a></p>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div><!--  class=\"top-wks-box\" -->\n\n\t</div><!--  class=\"top-wks-box-area\" -->\n</section><!-- class=\"top-works-area\" -->\n\n</article><!-- id=\"top-work\" -->\n\n\n<article id=\"top_interview-slider\" class=\"splide-btm\">\n<div class=\"no-scroll-x\"><!-- はみ出し防止 -->\n\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div id=\"s-intvw-title-box\">\n\t<div class=\"s-intvw-title\">\n\t\t<div class=\"lt-anime-area\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"title-b\"><span>はたらく人たち・スタッフインタビュー</span></p>\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"title-a\">JOPSの中の人</h2>\n\n\t\t\t<span class=\"line-pink-a\"></span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"line-green-a\"></span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"line-pink-b\"></span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"line-green-b\"></span>\n\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<p class=\"deco-en\">Staff <br class=\"d-md-none\">interview</p>\n\t</div>\n\t<p class=\"s-intvw-txt\">「JOPSの中の人」ってどんな人？<br>入社のきっかけや日々の仕事、感じているやりがいをご紹介します。</p>\n</div>\n</div><!-- class=\"container\" -->\n\n\n<section class=\"splide-intvw-area\">\n<div class=\"inner\">\n<div class=\"overflow-right\">\n\n<div class=\"splide js-intvw-slider\">\n\n<div class=\"splide__track\">\n\n\t<ul class=\"splide__list\">\n\t\t<li class=\"splide__slide\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"s-action\">\n\t\t\t<a href=\"/interview/staff-01/\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"staff-intvw-area\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"intvw-s-photo skshi\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"/common/images/interview/00-03-02-01-01.webp\" alt=\"staff-01\">\n\t\